* {{ill|Tammonji (Funabashi)|ja|多聞寺 (船橋市)|12=draft}} - A temple of the {{ill|Nichiren Buddhism|ja|Nichiren宗|12=draft}}, located in {{ill|Funabashi City|ja|船橋市|12=draft}}, [[Chiba Prefecture]]. * {{ill|Tammonji (Sumida)|ja|多聞寺 (墨田区)|12=draft}} - A temple of the {{ill|Chisan Sect of Shingon Buddhism|ja|真言宗智山派|1=Shingon-shū Chisan-ha|12=draft}}, located in {{ill|Sumida Ward|ja|墨田区|12=draft}}, [[Tokyo]]. * A former temple of the {{ill|Sōtō Sect|ja|曹洞宗|12=draft}} located in {{ill|Setagaya Ward|ja|世田谷区|12=draft}}, Tokyo (abolished). Refer to {{ill|Mishuku Shrine|ja|三宿神社|12=draft}}. * {{ill|Tammonji (Higashikurume)|ja|多聞寺 (東久留米市)|12=draft}} - A temple of the Chisan Sect of Shingon Buddhism, located in {{ill|Higashikurume City|ja|東久留米市|12=draft}}, Tokyo. * {{ill|Tammonji (Tarumi Ward, Kobe)|ja|多聞寺 (神戸市垂水区)|12=draft}} - A temple of the {{ill|Tendai Sect|ja|天台宗|12=draft}}, located in {{ill|Tarumi Ward|ja|垂水区|12=draft}}, [[Kobe City]], [[Hyōgo Prefecture]]. * {{ill|Tammonji (Kita Ward, Kobe)|ja|多聞寺 (神戸市北区)|12=draft}} - A temple of the {{ill|Shingon Sect|ja|真言宗|12=draft}}, located in {{ill|Kita Ward|ja|北区 (神戸市)|12=draft}}, Kobe City, Hyōgo Prefecture. * {{ill|Tammonji (Kasai)|ja|多聞寺 (加西市)|12=draft}} - A temple of the Sōtō Sect, located in {{ill|Kasai City|ja|加西市|12=draft}}, Hyōgo Prefecture. * {{ill|Tammonji (Tsurugi, Tokushima)|ja|多聞寺 (徳島県つるぎ町)|12=draft}} - A temple of the {{ill|Omuro Sect of Shingon Buddhism|ja|真言宗御室派|12=draft}}, located in {{ill|Tsurugi Town|ja|つるぎ町|12=draft}}, {{ill|Mima District|ja|美馬郡|12=draft}}, [[Tokushima Prefecture]]. * {{ill|Tammonji (Tonosho, Kagawa)|ja|多聞寺 (香川県土庄町)|12=draft}} - A temple of the {{ill|Koyasan Shingon Sect|ja|高野山真言宗|12=draft}}, located in {{ill|Tonosho Town|ja|土庄町|12=draft}}, {{ill|Shōzu District|ja|小豆郡|12=draft}}, [[Kagawa Prefecture]]. == See Also == * {{ill|Tammon-in|ja|多聞院|12=draft}} (disambiguation) {{Aimai}} <!--Tamonji-->
