'''Tammonji''' (多聞寺) refers to Buddhist temples in Japan.
* {{ill|Tammonji (Funabashi)|ja|多聞寺 (船橋市)|qq=draft|qq=draft}} - A temple of the {{ill|Nichiren Buddhism|ja|Nichiren宗|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, located in {{ill|Funabashi City|ja|船橋市|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, [[Chiba Prefecture]]. * {{ill|Tammonji (Sumida)|ja|多聞寺 (墨田区)|qq=draft|qq=draft}} - A temple of the {{ill|Chisan Sect of Shingon Buddhism|ja|真言宗智山派|1=Shingon-shū Chisan-ha|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, located in {{ill|Sumida Ward|ja|墨田区|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, [[Tokyo]]. * A former temple of the {{ill|Sōtō Sect|ja|曹洞宗|qq=draft|qq=draft}} located in {{ill|Setagaya Ward|ja|世田谷区|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, Tokyo (abolished). Refer to {{ill|Mishuku Shrine|ja|三宿神社|qq=draft|qq=draft}}. * {{ill|Tammonji (Higashikurume)|ja|多聞寺 (東久留米市)|qq=draft|qq=draft}} - A temple of the Chisan Sect of Shingon Buddhism, located in {{ill|Higashikurume City|ja|東久留米市|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, Tokyo. * {{ill|Tammonji (Tarumi Ward, Kobe)|ja|多聞寺 (神戸市垂水区)|qq=draft|qq=draft}} - A temple of the {{ill|Tendai Sect|ja|天台宗|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, located in {{ill|Tarumi Ward|ja|垂水区|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, [[Kobe City]], [[Hyōgo Prefecture]]. * {{ill|Tammonji (Kita Ward, Kobe)|ja|多聞寺 (神戸市北区)|qq=draft|qq=draft}} - A temple of the {{ill|Shingon Sect|ja|真言宗|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, located in {{ill|Kita Ward|ja|北区 (神戸市)|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, Kobe City, Hyōgo Prefecture. * {{ill|Tammonji (Kasai)|ja|多聞寺 (加西市)|qq=draft|qq=draft}} - A temple of the Sōtō Sect, located in {{ill|Kasai City|ja|加西市|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, Hyōgo Prefecture. * {{ill|Tammonji (Tsurugi, Tokushima)|ja|多聞寺 (徳島県つるぎ町)|qq=draft|qq=draft}} - A temple of the {{ill|Omuro Sect of Shingon Buddhism|ja|真言宗御室派|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, located in {{ill|Tsurugi Town|ja|つるぎ町|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, {{ill|Mima District|ja|美馬郡|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, [[Tokushima Prefecture]]. * {{ill|Tammonji (Tonosho, Kagawa)|ja|多聞寺 (香川県土庄町)|qq=draft|qq=draft}} - A temple of the {{ill|Koyasan Shingon Sect|ja|高野山真言宗|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, located in {{ill|Tonosho Town|ja|土庄町|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, {{ill|Shōzu District|ja|小豆郡|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, [[Kagawa Prefecture]]. == See Also == * {{ill|Tammon-in|ja|多聞院|qq=draft|qq=draft}} (disambiguation) {{disambiguation}}
