* {{ill|Tammonji (Funabashi)|ja|多聞寺 (船橋市)|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tammonji (Funabashi)|qq=}} - A temple of the {{ill|Nichiren Buddhism|ja|Nichiren宗|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Nichiren Buddhism|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}}, located in [[:en:Funabashi|Funabashi City]], [[:en:Chiba Prefecture|Chiba Prefecture]]. * {{ill|Tammonji (Sumida)|ja|多聞寺 (墨田区)|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tammonji (Sumida)|qq=}} - A temple of the [[:en:Shingon-shū Chisan-ha|Shingon-shū Chisan-ha]], located in [[:en:Sumida, Tokyo|Sumida Ward]], [[:en:Tokyo|Tokyo]]. * A former temple of the [[:en:Sōtō|Sōtō Sect]] located in [[:en:Setagaya|Setagaya Ward]], Tokyo (abolished). Refer to {{ill|Mishuku Shrine|ja|三宿神社|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Mishuku Shrine|qq=}}. * {{ill|Tammonji (Higashikurume)|ja|多聞寺 (東久留米市)|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tammonji (Higashikurume)|qq=}} - A temple of the Chisan Sect of Shingon Buddhism, located in [[:en:Higashikurume, Tokyo|Higashikurume City]], Tokyo. * {{ill|Tammonji (Tarumi Ward, Kobe)|ja|多聞寺 (神戸市垂水区)|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tammonji (Tarumi Ward, Kobe)|qq=}} - A temple of the [[:en:Tiantai|Tendai Sect]], located in [[:en:Tarumi-ku, Kobe|Tarumi Ward]], [[:en:Kobe City|Kobe City]], [[:en:Hyōgo Prefecture|Hyōgo Prefecture]]. * {{ill|Tammonji (Kita Ward, Kobe)|ja|多聞寺 (神戸市北区)|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tammonji (Kita Ward, Kobe)|qq=}} - A temple of the [[:en:Shingon Buddhism|Shingon Sect]], located in [[:en:Kita-ku, Kobe|Kita Ward]], Kobe City, Hyōgo Prefecture. * {{ill|Tammonji (Kasai)|ja|多聞寺 (加西市)|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tammonji (Kasai)|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} - A temple of the Sōtō Sect, located in [[:en:Kasai, Hyōgo|Kasai City]], Hyōgo Prefecture. * {{ill|Tammonji (Tsurugi, Tokushima)|ja|多聞寺 (徳島県つるぎ町)|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tammonji (Tsurugi, Tokushima)|qq=}}