e [[:en:Shingon Buddhism|Shingon Sect]], located in [[:en:Kita-ku, Kobe|Kita Ward]], Kobe City, Hyōgo Prefecture. * {{ill|Tammonji (Kasai)|ja|多聞寺 (加西市)|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tammonji (Kasai)|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} - A temple of the Sōtō Sect, located in [[:en:Kasai, Hyōgo|Kasai City]], Hyōgo Prefecture. * {{ill|Tammonji (Tsurugi, Tokushima)|ja|多聞寺 (徳島県つるぎ町)|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tammonji (Tsurugi, Tokushima)|qq=}} - A temple of the {{ill|Omuro Sect of Shingon Buddhism|ja|真言宗御室派|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Omuro Sect of Shingon Buddhism|qq=|1=Omuro school|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q420739}}, located in [[:en:Tsurugi, Tokushima|Tsurugi Town]], [[:en:Mima District, Tokushima|Mima District]], [[:en:Tokushima Prefecture|Tokushima Prefecture]]. * {{ill|Tammonji (Tonosho, Kagawa)|ja|多聞寺 (香川県土庄町)|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tammonji (Tonosho, Kagawa)|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} - A temple of the [[:en:Kōyasan Shingon-shū|Koyasan Shingon Sect]], located in [[:en:Tonoshō, Kagawa|Tonosho Town]], [[:en:Shōzu District, Kagawa|Shōzu District]], [[:en:Kagawa Prefecture|Kagawa Prefecture]]. == See Also == * {{ill|Tammon-in|ja|多聞院|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tammon-in|qq=|1=Tammon-in|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q11431014}} (disambiguation) {{disambiguation}}
